{"tid":612360,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《歐洲經濟》英國最新ILO失業率降至4.3% 1975年以來最低","createTime":"2018-03-31T18:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T18:58:56.000Z","uid":70274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d751c0d9f60fab017ea76405aca67a01c67da45d","tid":612360,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:55:45.000Z","msg":"AASTOCKS<br />\n<br />\n據英國國家統計局公布，截至今年1月的三個月按國際勞工組織(ILO)標準計算的失業率下降至4.3%，低於市場預估持平於前值4.4%，創1975年後逾四十年低位。<br />\n截至今年1月的三個月ILO就業人數增長加快至16.8萬人，較前值增長8.8萬人大幅增加，亦遠勝市場預估增長放緩至8.4萬人。(da/u)~<br />\n<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=kB73bLIf%2BAHZVGGCGCQ2qL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2043e9ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"c07d8b52b0eeb7e4f981a686cdbde0c6ebda9a6b","tid":612360,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:58:56.000Z","msg":"數據不可盡信"}]}